description:
Thomas Middleditch [Silicon Valley, B Positive, Penn Zero] is an actor, comedian, and screenwriter. Thomas joins Anna to talk about a proper smile, the influence of his favorite action movies, cultivating a sense of adventure, how a trip to Australia taught him about expectation, running your own race, the state of the world, and more.
